    <element name="Master Crafting" type="Class Feature" source="Final Fantasy XIV DND Compendium" id="ID_FFXIV_CLASS_FEATURE_MASTERCRAFTING">
        <description>
            <p>Beginning at the 12th level, after receiving and completing your guild quest, you will gain access to the Master Crafting Log.</p>
            <h5 class="caption">Advanced Melding</h5>
            <p>Your skill now allows you to meld 2 materia per item</p>
            <h5 class="caption">Desynthesis</h5>
            <p class="indent">You gain the ability to attempt to breakdown an item of the type that would appear in your crafting log. The difficulty is equal to the items crafting difficulty. On success you may select up to 2 crafting components to recover (does not include materia) but the item is lost, on failure the item and all components are lost.</p>
        </description>
